import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ApiService } from 'src/app/services/api.service'; import { Data } from '../../../model/interfaces.interface' @Component({ selector: 'app-dashboard', templateUrl: './dashboard.component.html', styleUrls: ['./dashboard.component.scss'] }) export class DashboardComponent implements OnInit { dataList: Data[] = []; constructor(private apiService: ApiService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.apiService.dashboard().subscribe( (response: Data) => { this.dataList.push(response); }, (error: any) => { console.error(error); } ); } }
